{
  "script_id": "cholesky",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "cholesky",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cholesky/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.06,
      "size": 32976,
      "text": "我们都熟悉把矩阵拆成下三角乘上三角的 LU 分解。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cholesky",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cholesky/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "但当矩阵既对称又正定时，它有一种更优雅的拆法。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cholesky",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cholesky/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "这就是 Cholesky 分解，可以看作 LU 分解的对称版本。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cholesky",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "define-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cholesky/xiaoxiao/define-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.42,
      "size": 38736,
      "text": "所谓对称，是指矩阵等于它自己的转置，沿主对角线镜像相同。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cholesky",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "define-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cholesky/xiaoxiao/define-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.37,
      "size": 37872,
      "text": "所谓正定，直观上是说它对应的二次型永远为正，不会塌陷。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cholesky",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "define-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cholesky/xiaoxiao/define-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.32,
      "size": 37152,
      "text": "满足这两个条件，矩阵就能唯一地写成一个下三角乘它的转置。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cholesky",
      "section_id": "formula",
      "line_id": "form-1",
      "filename": "formula-form-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cholesky/xiaoxiao/formula-form-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.27,
      "size": 20304,
      "text": "我们按列从左到右求下三角 L。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cholesky",
      "section_id": "formula",
      "line_id": "form-2",
      "filename": "formula-form-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cholesky/xiaoxiao/formula-form-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35424,
      "text": "对角元等于该位置的值减去左边已算平方和，再开平方根。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cholesky",
      "section_id": "formula",
      "line_id": "form-3",
      "filename": "formula-form-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cholesky/xiaoxiao/formula-form-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.34,
      "size": 37440,
      "text": "非对角元则减去对应行列已算乘积和，再除以上方的对角元。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cholesky",
      "section_id": "reconstruct",
      "line_id": "rec-1",
      "filename": "reconstruct-rec-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cholesky/xiaoxiao/reconstruct-rec-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.11,
      "size": 33696,
      "text": "把求出的 L 乘上它的转置，就会精确还原出原始矩阵 A。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cholesky",
      "section_id": "reconstruct",
      "line_id": "rec-2",
      "filename": "reconstruct-rec-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cholesky/xiaoxiao/reconstruct-rec-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.47,
      "size": 39456,
      "text": "如果计算中开方遇到非正的数，说明矩阵并不正定，分解无法进行。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cholesky",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cholesky/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "拖动进度条，看 L 的每个元素是怎样一格一格被算出来的。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cholesky",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cholesky/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.31,
      "size": 37008,
      "text": "切换不同的正定矩阵，观察 A 分解成 L 与 L 转置的全过程。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cholesky",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cholesky/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "Cholesky 把对称正定矩阵分解为下三角乘它的转置。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cholesky",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cholesky/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.3,
      "size": 36864,
      "text": "它计算量小、数值稳定，是求解方程组和随机采样的利器。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "cholesky",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/cholesky/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.5,
      "size": 24048,
      "text": "记住这个对称之美的分解，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
